autodetect.description:
Home Assistant areas that contain a temperature sensor are listed below. Confirm to create a default daily profile (if none exists yet), floors (from your Home Assistant floors) and one area per detected room.

Already-configured areas are left untouched. Heating/cooling actuators are never guessed — add them afterwards. ↩ marks a floor that already exists; ⚠️ marks a room with more than one temperature sensor, so double-check which one was picked.

{summary}
